metadata.description:
The grand prize is $531

Choose the prettiest portrait of a woman - buying the first NFT you will get a 1% reward. The next person will get a reward for buying 2 NFT and will get a 2% reward

Reward system:
Rewards are paid out by a smart contract in the Fibonacci system 1% 2% 3% 5% 8% 13% 21% 34% 51% 85%

You can immediately put your NFT up for sale, thanks to which you will receive a reward in your wallet and you will earn by resell a little cheaper than the next NFT price.

And the most important! GRAND PRIZE for collecting all 100 NFTs into one wallet:
The grand prize is $531.
So 40,000 ART is 0.4ETH (at the current ETH exchange rate on 12/14/2022 $1328)
